#EXTINF:267 tvg-logo="https://cdn2.suno.ai/video_upload_d65022a3-da22-498d-9115-bdb28d47ac21_video_upload_d65022a3-da22-498d-9115-bdb28d47ac21_cover_snapshot_0s_1761753603_image.jpeg" group-title="Genre: Dark Bubblegum Pop-Noir Ballad, Ethereal Gothic Pop. Mood: Profoundly unsettling, fragile, desperate, suffocating, yet strangely captivating. The sound of internal despair presented with a disturbing, delicate facade. Designed to powerfully convey mental health struggle. Tempo: Slow, haunting minor key (around 80-90 BPM). Vocal Style: A primary, **extremely breathy, fragile, almost whispered Female Lead Vocal**, imbued with raw intimacy and deep vulnerability. Occasional moments of strained, almost cracking delivery. Features **sparse, ethereal, distorted Female Backing Vocals** that sound like fragmented thoughts or distant cries for help. Instrumentation: Deep, **heavy, pulsing synth bass** that creates a sense of dread and internal pressure. A crisp, **brittle, almost mechanical drum machine beat** that feels relentless and inescapable, emphasizing isolation. Ethereal, **cold, slightly dissonant synth pads** that expand and contract, creating a vast yet suffocating space.",𝒫𝒾𝓍𝒾𝑒 𝐵𝓁𝓊 ♡ - Drowning ~
