#EXTINF:247 tvg-logo="https://cdn2.suno.ai/image_26970975-3b21-4d95-8afc-947ec381ef09.jpeg" group-title="Genre: Gritty London Blues, Cockney Blues Storytelling, British Rhythm & Blues. Mood: Raw, down-on-your-luck, resilient, slightly desperate, ultimately hopeful, and deeply authentic to a working-class London narrative. Tempo: Mid-tempo, shuffling blues groove (around 90-110 BPM). Vocal Style: A primary, **gruff, storytelling Male Lead Vocal with a strong, authentic Cockney London accent**. Delivery is conversational, world-weary, yet with a underlying resilience. Features **occasional rough, male backing vocal chants** for emphasis. Instrumentation: - Dominant: **Dirty, distorted electric slide guitar** with a wailing, expressive tone. **Gritty, raw blues harmonica** provides soulful counter-melodies and expressive wails. - Rhythm Section: A tight, **driving blues drum beat** (heavy kick, snappy snare, prominent hi-hat shuffle) that feels grounded and rhythmic. A thick, **pulsing electric bassline** provides a solid, unwavering foundation.",𝒫𝒾𝓍𝒾𝑒 𝐵𝓁𝓊 ♡ - Diesel Dave
